{"type":"message","id":"e247e25d","parentId":"891464ea","timestamp":"2026-04-23T03:34:42.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经按那篇文章的思路给你做了一个可复用的生图 skill，放在这里：\n\n- `skills/cliproxyapi-image-skill/SKILL.md`\n- `skills/cliproxyapi-image-skill/references/config-notes.md`\n- `skills/cliproxyapi-image-skill/scripts/generate_image.py`\n\n核心能力是这几个：\n\n- 把 `gpt-5.4-mini` 之类的 Codex 模型别名成 `gpt-image-1024x1024` 这类“伪生图模型”\n- 通过 CLIProxyAPI 的 `payload.override-raw` 强制注入 `image_generation`\n- 提供一个最小 Python 脚本，直接请求 `/v1/responses` 并把返回的 base64 图片落盘\n\n你可以直接这样用：\n\n```bash\npython3 skills/cliproxyapi-image-skill/scripts/generate_image.py \\\n  --api-url https://your-cliproxyapi.example.com/v1/responses \\\n  --api-key sk-xxx \\\n  --model gpt-image-1536x1024 \\\n  --prompt \"画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有霓虹灯和中文招牌\" \\\n  --output ./generated.png\n```\n\n补充两点：\n- 我尝试顺手提交 git，但这个 workspace 当前不是 git 仓库，所以没法 commit。\n- 如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你把这个 skill 打磨成“可直接安装到 `~/.openclaw/skills/` 的正式版”，顺手再加一个 `curl`/PowerShell 示例版本。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e9934be564819786fee2b77c8b8daf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":42672,"output":361,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43033,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776915273140,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e9934a85088197bc66616c1ea999d7"}}
