{"type":"message","id":"280ebd01","parentId":"0b5a8e0c","timestamp":"2026-04-23T03:34:53.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"那个异步命令其实只是我前面拿文章正文时留下的抓取进程，结果还是被 Cloudflare 挡住了。  \n它返回的是挑战页脚本片段，不是正文内容，所以对你这边没有新增有效信息。\n\n不过没耽误正事，我已经用可用镜像拿到了文章核心内容，并把 skill 做好了。  \n如果你要，我现在可以继续两步之一：\n\n1. 把这个 skill 安装到你本机的 `~/.openclaw/skills/` 目录  \n2. 再帮你补一个更完整版本，比如支持多尺寸、多 prompt 模板、批量出图","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e9935a42308197add7b622057a5e59\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":43185,"output":146,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776915287262,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99358b1d88197a41a8c24b64bacaf"}}
