{"type":"message","id":"bc766720","parentId":"1fe02c60","timestamp":"2026-04-23T03:38:23.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定了，我已经帮你继续做完了：\n\n**已完成**\n- 已打包 skill：`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/dist/cliproxyapi-image-skill.skill`\n- 已安装到本地 skills 目录：`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/cliproxyapi-image-skill`\n\n**本地安装内容**\n- `SKILL.md`\n- `references/config-notes.md`\n- `scripts/generate_image.py`\n\n**你现在可以做的事**\n1. 以后直接把这个 skill 当成你的本地 skill 用\n2. 用里面的脚本直接调 CLIProxyAPI 生图\n\n示例命令：\n\n```bash\npython3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/cliproxyapi-image-skill/scripts/generate_image.py \\\n  --api-url https://your-cliproxyapi.example.com/v1/responses \\\n  --api-key sk-xxx \\\n  --model gpt-image-1536x1024 \\\n  --prompt \"画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有霓虹灯和中文招牌\" \\\n  --output ./generated.png\n```\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你补两样，很实用：\n- **直接生成一份 CLIProxyAPI 配置片段**，你复制进去就能用\n- **把这个 skill 升级成更强版**，支持多尺寸预设、批量 prompt、生图失败自动诊断","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99428d11481978bc72fba460b704d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":45942,"output":344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46286,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776915494011,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e9942764208197bafdb2dc99732c4f"}}
