{"type":"message","id":"9baf4731","parentId":"967e3c06","timestamp":"2026-04-23T03:45:00.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"那现在就真的可以用了，太好了 👍\n\n你直接跑这个就行：\n\n```bash\npython3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/cliproxyapi-image-skill/scripts/generate_image.py \\\n  --api-url https://你的CLIProxyAPI地址/v1/responses \\\n  --api-key 你的apikey \\\n  --model gpt-image-1536x1024 \\\n  --prompt \"画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有霓虹灯和中文招牌\" \\\n  --output ./generated.png\n```\n\n如果你的配置没问题，成功后它会输出生成图片的绝对路径。\n\n你也可以先试这几个 model：\n\n- `gpt-image-1024x1024`\n- `gpt-image-1024x1536`\n- `gpt-image-1536x1024`\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以直接帮你做一次**真实测试出图**。你只要把：\n- API 地址\n- API key\n- 想画的 prompt\n\n发我，我就直接帮你跑。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e995b855208197b3b51550cb717dd7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":818,"output":243,"cacheRead":46208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47269,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776915891211,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e995b492b08197919c41678e844b2a"}}
