{"type":"message","id":"422c7116","parentId":"761d4a17","timestamp":"2026-04-23T03:53:59.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，我给你一份**可直接替换的完整配置**，你把原文件备份后整体换成这个，再重启 CLIProxyAPI 就行：\n\n```yaml\nhost: \"\"\nport: 8317\n\nauth-dir: \"/root/.cli-proxy-api\"\n\napi-keys:\n  - 48ch-wzC2qzxmQIBPq8mMXbQXRi454v8\n\nremote-management:\n  allow-remote: true\n  secret-key: \"$2a$10$7WnG.OgYSfXfrgvKblhFg.lOv82Xk/cRllxO7tj08WlUpVacOQqGe\"\n  disable-control-panel: false\n\nrequest-retry: 3\n\nquota-exceeded:\n  switch-project: true\n  switch-preview-model: true\n  antigravity-credits: true\n\nlogging-to-file: true\nlogs-max-total-size-mb: 200\nws-auth: true\ndebug: true\n\noauth-model-alias:\n  codex:\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n      fork: true\n\npayload:\n  override-raw:\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\":\"image_generation\"}'\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\",\"size\":\"1024x1024\",\"quality\":\"high\",\"background\":\"auto\"}]'\n\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\":\"image_generation\"}'\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\",\"size\":\"1024x1536\",\"quality\":\"high\",\"background\":\"auto\"}]'\n\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\":\"image_generation\"}'\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\",\"size\":\"1536x1024\",\"quality\":\"high\",\"background\":\"auto\"}]'\n\nopenai-compatibility:\n  - name: openAi\n    base-url: http://69.63.219.95:8080/v1\n    api-key-entries:\n      - api-key: [REDACTED]    models:\n      - name: gpt-5.4\n      - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n```\n\n然后做这 3 步：\n\n1. **备份原配置**\n2. **替换成上面这份**\n3. **重启 CLIProxyAPI**\n\n如果你是命令行启动的，重启后再跑我们刚才那个命令测试。\n\n你改完直接回我一句：\n**“改好了，继续测”**\n\n我就继续帮你验证出图。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e997ca7f18819787f9c05cdbc2d0e4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":52320,"output":715,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53035,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776916423687,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e997c906648197a78c035d03c2cfa9"}}
