{"type":"message","id":"c71a37f3","parentId":"c66d9379","timestamp":"2026-04-23T04:07:01.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你在服务器本机直接跑这条，先做最小验证：\n\n```bash\ncurl -s http://127.0.0.1:8317/v1/responses \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer [REDACTED_TOKEN]' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"gpt-image-1536x1024\",\n    \"input\": [{\n      \"type\": \"message\",\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [{\n        \"type\": \"input_text\",\n        \"text\": \"画一张赛博朋克夜景，要有霓虹灯和中文招牌\"\n      }]\n    }],\n    \"stream\": false,\n    \"store\": false\n  }'\n```\n\n然后看返回结果：\n\n### 如果还是这个错\n```json\nTool choice 'image_generation' not found in 'tools' parameter\n```\n说明：\n- alias 命中了\n- 但 `payload.override-raw` 没注进去，或者这条链路根本不支持\n\n### 如果返回了别的错\n把完整返回贴我，我继续判断。\n\n### 如果成功\n会返回一个大 JSON，里面应该能找到类似：\n- `image_generation_call`\n- `result`\n- `output_format`\n\n如果你方便，最好再同时执行一条日志查看：\n\n```bash\ntail -n 100 /root/.cli-proxy-api/*.log\n```\n\n或者如果你的 CLIProxyAPI 是 systemd 跑的：\n\n```bash\njournalctl -u cliproxyapi -n 100 --no-pager\n```\n\n你把 **curl 返回** 或 **日志输出** 贴给我，我继续帮你收口。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99ade852481979ae928d6f7efd150\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":55159,"output":385,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55544,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776917211377,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99adcad248197a9fabc6a6be431be"}}
