{"type":"message","id":"b20da118","parentId":"b183657a","timestamp":"2026-04-23T04:13:44.230Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"那就很清楚了，用 Docker 最省事。\n\n你现在直接做这套：\n\n## 1. 先拉最新版镜像\n```bash\ndocker pull ghcr.io/jingkaihe/cli-proxy-api:latest\n```\n\n## 2. 停掉旧容器\n先看名字：\n```bash\ndocker ps\n```\n\n然后停掉旧的那个，比如假设容器名叫 `cli-proxy-api`：\n\n```bash\ndocker stop cli-proxy-api\ndocker rm cli-proxy-api\n```\n\n## 3. 用原来的配置重新起最新版\n如果你的配置文件在宿主机，比如 `/root/cli-proxy-api/config.yaml`，可以这样启动：\n\n```bash\ndocker run -d \\\n  --name cli-proxy-api \\\n  -p 8317:8317 \\\n  -v /root/cli-proxy-api/config.yaml:/app/config.yaml \\\n  -v /root/.cli-proxy-api:/root/.cli-proxy-api \\\n  ghcr.io/jingkaihe/cli-proxy-api:latest\n```\n\n## 4. 看版本和日志\n```bash\ndocker logs cli-proxy-api --tail 100\n```\n\n## 5. 再跑最小测试\n```bash\ncurl -s http://127.0.0.1:8317/v1/responses \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer [REDACTED_TOKEN]' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"gpt-image-1536x1024\",\n    \"input\": [{\n      \"type\": \"message\",\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [{\n        \"type\": \"input_text\",\n        \"text\": \"画一张赛博朋克夜景，要有霓虹灯和中文招牌\"\n      }]\n    }],\n    \"stream\": false,\n    \"store\": false\n  }'\n```\n\n---\n\n## 重点提醒\n你原来的挂载路径要确认一下，尤其是这两个：\n- 配置文件路径\n- OAuth 凭证目录路径\n\n如果容器里程序实际读的不是 `/app/config.yaml`，那启动命令要按你的原容器来改。\n\n**最稳的办法**是你先把这条发我：\n\n```bash\ndocker inspect cli-proxy-api\n```\n\n或者至少发我：\n\n```bash\ndocker ps --format 'table {{.Names}}\\t{{.Image}}\\t{{.Ports}}'\ndocker inspect cli-proxy-api --format '{{json .Mounts}}'\n```\n\n我可以直接帮你把**你这台机器可用的 docker run 命令**拼好，避免你重建时挂载错了。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99c6d13008197a1afcff01423ae93\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":57001,"output":603,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776917609536,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99c6b3180819789c9264f18109733"}}
