{"type":"message","id":"fc2bb42c","parentId":"b0f2a576","timestamp":"2026-04-23T04:22:44.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"对，就是这个仓库。  \n那我们现在基本可以按它的最新版路线走，不用再绕了。\n\n你下一步最值的是直接确认**你当前容器到底用的是什么镜像名**，因为升级 Docker 时最怕拉错仓库名。\n\n请在服务器执行这两条，然后发我结果：\n\n```bash\ndocker ps --format 'table {{.Names}}\\t{{.Image}}\\t{{.Status}}\\t{{.Ports}}'\ndocker inspect $(docker ps -q --filter name=cli) --format '{{.Name}} -> {{.Config.Image}}'\n```\n\n如果你懒得筛容器名，也可以直接：\n\n```bash\ndocker ps\n```\n\n我拿到后会直接给你一套**可复制执行的升级命令**，包括：\n- pull 最新镜像\n- 停旧容器\n- 保留原配置和 auth-dir\n- 重建容器\n- 验证版本\n- 再测生图\n\n现在这一步已经很接近收口了。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99e9082b4819794a08f86312c6105\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":60555,"output":226,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60781,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776918155694,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99e8e8dd881978c96262fe160bda7"}}
