{"type":"message","id":"7f28aef1","parentId":"230937ea","timestamp":"2026-04-23T04:25:19.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我这边不能直接访问你那台服务器的 Docker，所以没法替你查看。  \n但你只要在服务器上跑一条，我就能接着帮你：\n\n```bash\ndocker ps --format 'table {{.Names}}\\t{{.Image}}\\t{{.Status}}\\t{{.Ports}}'\n```\n\n如果你愿意，再补一条更完整的：\n\n```bash\ndocker inspect <容器名> --format '{{json .Mounts}}'\n```\n\n你把输出贴给我，我就直接帮你拼成**可执行的升级命令**，不用你自己猜。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99f2cc6d881978b3e0735b0e3dea6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":61450,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61583,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776918312564,"responseId":"resp_0e1a3cd01f34f22f0169e99f2b055c819788adff329f89fefb"}}
